msgstr "5. Links von Drittanbietern"

#: .\matches\templates\matches\terms_of_use.html:38
msgid ""
"Our site may contain links to third-party websites (such as advertisers or "
"partners). We have no control over the content or privacy practices of those "
"sites and assume no responsibility for them."
msgstr ""
"Unsere Website kann Links zu Websites Dritter enthalten (z. B. "
